text: Talat Xhaferi or Talat Dzaferi (; born 15 April 1962) is a Macedonian politician and the Prime Minister of North Macedonia from January 2024 until June 2024. He was previously the President of the Assembly of the Republic of North Macedonia from 2017 until 2024. Category:Presidents of North Macedonia Category:1962 births Category:Living people
title: Talat Xhaferi
